I had been invited to an exclusive preview of Alfred Kcirbuk's new film, "The Morning Shall Come".

LineNo: 4550409,

Narrator: With its massive budget and Kcirbuk...

With its massive budget and Kcirbuk's directorial cachet, this drama was set to be a milestone for Sordland's burgeoning film scene. Personally, though, I was just looking forward to spending some time with my family.
